title: Intervention S02E21 - Lauren
description: Lauren! Once a teacher, now a burnout with a predilection toward tie-dye shirts...and a hankering for heroin. She is volatile, emotionally abusive, and fascinating. Truly, she is a study in the depths that addiction can take people that, at one point, were functioning normally. A well-adjusted youth, college graduate, and athlete, we see Lauren transform into a moody malcontent, willing to trample over her own mother to get her fix. Intervention, season 2, episode 21.
